This is a modified Monospace for heroku cedar, using Postgres, and updated for some Rails 3.2.2 action.

Find a test app on Heroku Cedar stack @ http://subscribetest.herokuapp.com/ 

Installation steps:
* You will need a publishable token and a secret token. Add them both to config/initializers/stripe.rb.
* Install the bundler gem if you don't already have it
* Run the command "bundle" from the root of this project
* Run the command "rake db:migrate" from the root of this project
* Run the command "rails s"

